Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.35,0:00:20.76,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.76,0:00:22.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:29.90,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.24,0:00:40.56,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.56,0:00:43.98,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:49.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.52,0:00:55.74,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:01:02.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.75,0:01:07.25,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.25,0:01:09.33,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.33,0:01:16.51,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.58,0:01:27.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.03,0:01:30.23,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:35.78,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:41.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, let's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:49.04,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:53.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:55.79,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.79,0:02:00.15,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.15,0:02:02.85,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:04.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.52,0:02:06.23,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:07.89,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:09.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.06,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.06,0:02:12.98,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:14.59,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.59,0:02:15.76,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.76,0:02:20.02,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.02,0:02:22.20,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:26.58,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.86,0:02:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:29.00,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:33.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.11,0:02:35.49,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.49,0:02:39.90,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:43.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.89,0:02:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.00,0:02:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight desperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.56,0:02:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.81,0:03:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned to rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,0:03:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become the next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.49,0:03:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends overcome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.40,0:03:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and less able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.47,0:03:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.83,0:03:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure is waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.17,0:03:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.32,0:03:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the Grand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While Buggy and Mr. 3 ascended to level 4 in order to break out,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.25,0:03:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the moribund Luffy was injected with a Healing Hormone by Ivankov,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.94,0:03:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which will cure him, but rob him of 10 years of life!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.66,0:03:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Food!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.31,0:03:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.16,0:04:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...recovered!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.21,0:04:10.70,Ep Title,,0000,0000,0000,,"Luffy's Back! Ivan-san Begins the Breakout Plan!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! He absorbed all the energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.78,0:04:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a guy! You must be superhuman!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.87,0:04:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has overcome Magellan's poison! I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.85,0:04:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He recovered after only 20 hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.11,0:04:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miracle? It's something far greater than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.26,0:04:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it! You did it! You did it! You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it! You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.39,0:05:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.51,0:05:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Bon-chan! I'm so happy you survived!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.58,0:05:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Are you kidding?! Gimme a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.78,0:05:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one that made me worry....
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.23,0:05:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon-chan! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.23,0:05:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You alright?! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.26,0:05:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to you? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.71,0:05:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just exhausted! But it's not because of his wounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.99,0:05:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Ivan-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ivan-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.03,0:05:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made it! Thank you for helping both of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.99,0:05:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna thank someone, you better thank Mr. 2 Bon boy, not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.81,0:05:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only nudged you along with my powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But him,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.64,0:05:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he was struggling alongside you for hours and hours and hours here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.21,0:06:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He lost his voice and spewed up blood but he didn't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.61,0:06:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He kept shouting "Hang in there!" "You have to live!" to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.83,0:06:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it somehow affected your recovery!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.27,0:06:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.54,0:06:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What's wrong with him?\N--Is he naked?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.27,0:06:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw-chan, I come to rescue you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the name of friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.23,0:06:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell is this guy all covered in blood?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.96,0:06:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Earlier, I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.47,0:06:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry that I ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.77,0:07:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.83,0:07:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm his friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.17,0:07:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw-chan! I'm not gonna let you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.53,0:07:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon-chan, thank you! I'm really grateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,0:07:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here are your hat and clothes. But you're not ready yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.17,0:07:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to rest for several days to be fully recovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.93,0:07:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time! I've already wasted too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.33,0:08:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but can you look after Bon-chan? I'll be back for him later!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, hey!\N--See? You're not completely well yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.49,0:08:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The paper is still pointing down! Ace must be downstairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, where am I now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.59,0:08:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.43,0:08:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Vivre Card, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.01,0:08:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're on a floor between level 5 and 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet that since you've recovered,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.06,0:08:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you wanna go to rescue your brother no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.98,0:08:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's your life! You can do whatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.35,0:08:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Ivan-chan? Are you gonna break out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon-chan thought he'd help your butt get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.82,0:08:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your butt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.03,0:08:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you guide me to Ace on your way out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.36,0:08:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say? Bon boy came here to save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.41,0:09:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I didn't know that. That's really sweet of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.54,0:09:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't need to be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.71,0:09:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not time to break out yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.01,0:09:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what's going on in the world now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.96,0:09:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world is about to change with the Navy and the Whitebeard Pirates as major players!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.85,0:09:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's not gonna make a move yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.43,0:09:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the mastermind of all revolutionaries in the world and my comrade!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The revolutionary--Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.50,0:09:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're talking about my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. When your father makes a move with his army,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.34,0:09:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then I'll reappear and enter the world again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.93,0:09:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I escaped now, I'd just end up on countless wanted lists around the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-D-D-D... Dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.28,0:10:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he say "my dad?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.41,0:10:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.99,0:10:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.89,0:10:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...your dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.88,0:10:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-D-D-Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.06,0:10:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a son of Dragon?! He has a son?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.67,0:10:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I shouldn't have said anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.03,0:10:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's okay. Grandpa didn't keep it a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.55,0:10:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father's name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.16,0:10:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Monkey D. Dragon! He's a revolutionary!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.05,0:10:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know about him. I've never even seen his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.94,0:10:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This seems legitimate!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.37,0:10:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't seem to be the kind to lie and he's a new star in the world of pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I've just seen his extraordinary vital force!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.54,0:11:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not a normal man! So it's believable!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.71,0:11:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you come from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.25,0:11:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm from the East Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.39,0:11:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever you go for some air,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.06,0:11:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you always face towards the same direction no matter where you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.44,0:11:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I? Why would you be so curious about such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.05,0:11:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.59,0:11:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, it must be a homing instinct like animals have.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.24,0:11:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is your home in that direction?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.81,0:11:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're thinking about your family in the east,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.54,0:11:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.19,0:11:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so inquisitive about my past, Ivan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.95,0:11:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.55,0:11:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! If Straw boy is a son of Dragon for real, that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.03,0:12:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inazuma, check to see when they'll take Ace boy away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.81,0:12:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.43,0:12:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't much time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.12,0:12:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Vivre Card was pointing down which means that he's still here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.19,0:12:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go to level 6 with Straw boy now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are you gonna show me the way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.79,0:12:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, did you just say "level 6?" Isn't it 5?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.80,0:12:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be! You're on level 5.5!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever. Alright, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.25,0:12:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't paying attention! It didn't even occur to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Straw boy is Dragon's son, so is Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.05,0:12:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this why the Navy captured Ace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.07,0:12:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it can't be! There would be no point in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.72,0:12:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't wanna fight Whitebeard and Dragon at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.59,0:12:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does the government truly want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.31,0:13:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, it's time to make a move!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.07,0:13:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Bon-chan! I'll be back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.96,0:13:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell anyone casually about your birth!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.07,0:13:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.53,0:13:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a friend of your dad and one of the commanders of the Revolutionaries army!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.30,0:13:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I was arrested!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.35,0:13:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's my duty to support you whether you like it or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let my friend's son die before my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.71,0:13:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell all the people in the New Kama Land!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.09,0:13:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to rescue Ace boy and try to break out of the prison!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.98,0:13:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What are you saying all of the sudden?\N--Isn't this a bit hasty?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Decisions must always be sudden!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.66,0:13:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna come with me, get ready to die,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.06,0:13:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,prepare for action and wait for us here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.77,0:14:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.28,0:14:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll follow you, Ivan-sama, to the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a new beginning for New Kama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Wait for me, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.04,0:14:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.21,0:14:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His pulse...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.50,0:14:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.99,0:14:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His pulse...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.07,0:15:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.92,0:15:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a joke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.43,0:15:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because the treatment has just shortened his life,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.67,0:15:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he must be exhausted still on some level!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.65,0:15:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Emporio...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.15,0:15:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Energy Hormone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.89,0:15:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a matter of adrenaline!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you have enough energy for a day!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll feel the after effects in several days but I guess it won't matter much at that point!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.21,0:15:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Warden! Warden won't like it if he hears that you've been sitting there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:16:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be sure to tell him later!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.19,0:16:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are so mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.87,0:16:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. 2, Mr. 3, Buggy the Clown...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.33,0:16:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure that they got onto level 5?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.12,0:16:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, his disguise was perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.50,0:16:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the only thing that they found on level 5 was the headdress covered in blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.99,0:16:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We assume that they took Straw Hat out of the cell
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.76,0:16:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but ended up being eaten by the wolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.73,0:16:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.63,0:16:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought that I'd wear this special order thing before I became the warden.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.03,0:16:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still haven't brought down Magellan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.45,0:16:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say it so plainly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.04,0:16:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we get duped or beaten again,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.84,0:16:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,both yours and the Warden's jobs are on the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.60,0:16:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My position, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.93,0:16:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Of course!\N--Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.95,0:16:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Staircase to level 3 must be close!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.26,0:17:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Level 4 is a breeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.09,0:17:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen any jailers at all! They're totally gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.93,0:17:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make a game of it! It's the Buggy and 3 Adventures!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.15,0:17:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop suddenly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.70,0:17:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Surveillance Transponder Snail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.50,0:17:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it finds us, all our efforts will go to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.12,0:17:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for noticing it, partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.98,0:17:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go carefully from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.19,0:17:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.86,0:17:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My eyes are itchy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.47,0:17:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be Magellan's poison!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.45,0:18:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That poison that he used against Straw Hat is still in the air here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.71,0:18:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.58,0:18:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guards will see us through it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.43,0:18:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That was close.\N--That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:19.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,THE ELEVATOR TO LEVEL 6
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.29,0:18:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so strict, Domino.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.92,0:18:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to do your business quickly from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.17,0:18:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.07,0:18:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.36,0:18:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.78,0:18:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.10,0:18:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to hand them the prisoner 9 am sharp at the front gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.46,0:18:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.73,0:18:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can't make it, we'll ruin the honor of Impel Down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.64,0:18:52.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,THE FRONT GATE OF IMPEL DOWN
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.99,0:18:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! We'll take Portgaz D. Ace from here and get to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:19:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Marineford--Navy Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.34,0:19:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until the very moment that we hand over the prisoner,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.58,0:19:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I need you to pay full attention!\N--Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.94,0:19:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be prepared for any possibility, we'll convey him strictly with 5 ships...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.74,0:19:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...under the direction of 5 vice admirals! Do not fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.18,0:19:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.25,0:19:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno why but I'm full of energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.51,0:19:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta hurry! We don't wanna waste even a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.06,0:19:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no security here! So we can just run out in the open!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing can stop us now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.29,0:19:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.11,0:19:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.60,0:19:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That looks like Ivankov! I thought that he was dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.44,0:19:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.34,0:20:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Death...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.58,0:20:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Wink!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.31,0:20:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inazuma, open it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.97,0:20:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.03,0:20:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll be monitoring us from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.23,0:20:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come and get me if you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.49,0:20:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have an intruder!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.81,0:20:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're at the staircase between level 5 and 6!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.86,0:20:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I know this big guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.75,0:20:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was the king of queers--Ivankov who went missing years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.07,0:20:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could this be possible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.10,0:20:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did he survive all these years?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.71,0:20:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is the invader from yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.62,0:20:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that he was killed by the Warden!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.06,0:21:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he's another missing prisoner!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.87,0:21:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A revolutionary from South Blue--Inazuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.83,0:21:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.44,0:21:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're heading straight to level 6!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.84,0:21:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They want to save "Fire Fist" Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.33,0:21:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Domino-san and Warden Magellan are also heading to level 6 now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.06,0:21:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll bump into each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.32,0:21:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are all alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.81,0:21:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Warden!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.89,0:21:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Activate passageway traps now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.66,0:21:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call jailers on level 6 and have them clear for action!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.89,0:21:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They need to hold on until Sadie-chan and the demon guards get there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.85,0:21:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And report this to Warden Magellan and all floors!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.27,0:21:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's all! Hurry up!\N--Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.43,0:21:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen Vice Warden getting so serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.86,0:21:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's an imposter again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.79,0:21:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.93,0:21:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My job is on the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.40,0:21:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he's the real one!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.65,0:21:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can make it! We can make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.82,0:22:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be there right away, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.43,0:22:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, Portgaz D. Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.49,0:23:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will take you to Marineford...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.38,0:23:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...where the execution ground is!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.77,0:23:09.98,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,The public execution of Ace is in...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.98,0:23:12.00,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,...6 hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.00,0:23:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.37,0:23:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy finally makes it to the \Nlowest level of Impel Down, level 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.88,0:23:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, Ace has already been taken away, \Nand the cell is empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.51,0:23:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy tries to follow Ace but he's held up by Hannyabal's traps!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.89,0:23:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.39,0:23:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ace's Convoy Begins! \NBattle on the Lowest Floor Level 6!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.30,0:23:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
